Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Mission Trails Regional Park - Old Mission Dam
Description: A beautiful, old Spanish dam that is made out of old stones that blocks a river that runs through the wooded area of the park.

Name: Hume Lake
Description: A lake up in the Sierra Nevadas where my friends and me have gone to have summer camp. There is a dam and a river that feeds into the lake, as well as a lot of hiking trails and other fun activities on the grounds.

Name: Convict Lake
Description: A lake in the Mammoth area that has beautiful hiking trails around it, typically well stocked with fish for fishing, as well as a beautiful apsen grove in the back which is my favorite part of the lake.

Name: Mahekal Beach Resort (Quintana Roo, Mexico)
Description: A resort situated on the Gulf of Mexico in Playa del Carmen. It is a beautiful resort with beach bungaloos and a variety of wildlife and partylife. The resort is right on the beach and is situated in the city of Playa del Carmen

Name: Torrey Pines Golf Course - South Course
Description: PGA level golf course situated on the Torrey Pines bluffs above the Pacific Ocean. It is a two coursed golf course, with a north and south, the south course being my favorite.
